        "title": "Exchange Nailing for Femoral Nonunion",
        "definition": "Reamed exchange intramedullary nailing with larger diameter nail for femoral shaft nonunion.",
        "summary": "Dynamization alone may suffice for hypertrophic tibial nonunion; femoral atrophic often needs graft."
      },
